{"tid":264671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子浮屍鯉魚門石灘 手纏繩綁石塊","createTime":"2017-05-31T04:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T06:01:30.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"71f73aaf990e7d0edf1dba1faa9fc9eb2b677df3","tid":264671,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:22:03.000Z","msg":"早上6時許，一名男子被發現在鯉魚門馬環村石灘近岸處，載浮載沉。消防員到場將該名男子救上岸，但經檢驗證實他已告身亡。死者穿著一條深色短褲，50歲至60歲，身材略胖，<span style=\"color: red;\">雙手用尼龍繩纏着石塊</span>，其中右手的石塊甩脫。現場石罅內，發現相信是死者的遺物，包括一件上衣、銀包、證件及一張字條。有街坊稱，昨日傍晚6時已見到該些財物。<br />\n<br />\n警方隨後找來死者兩名女親友，確定死者身份，<span style=\"color: red;\">初步調查事件沒有可疑。</span><br />\n<br />\n發現男浮屍的婦人稱，她14歲的兒子出村口返學，途中見到該男子在海面漂浮，於是跑回家通知她，再致電報警。事後她向死者遺體合什喃喃自語。<br />\n<br />\n正當警員在場調查期間，約20分鐘後，距離現場約50米外，一名老婦懷疑遇溺，面部朝天，與她同行的女友人發現，連忙高聲呼救，並將她拉上岸，由跑到來的救護員替她急救，隨後送院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n有泳客表示，老婦家住油塘，隨兩名朋友到來在淺水區玩水：「落水幾個字啫，響水邊都無游出去」；也有泳客指，老婦在水深及膝的位置暈倒，跌在水中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56763171&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170531\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56763171%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170531&d=Jlyqv5s1JpooMF7Os7siI3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=a22da2a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56763171%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170531&h=1dd9026a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56763171&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170531</a>"},{"pid":"77e119f3a5de3816e4839007fe7171516c000247","tid":264671,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:23:36.000Z","msg":"又嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d9183fc17eb2a5a40f886490119380c5b86cdd","tid":264671,"uid":23785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:25:36.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣都無可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"dea1c9ff2de33a250a8a6e7c351e069389a22159","tid":264671,"uid":39576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:27:43.000Z","msg":"連登神探全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1725fc51512cc41d1a3e96febfc4e2ed00edd39","tid":264671,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:54:27.000Z","msg":"發現相信是死者的遺物，包括一件上衣、銀包、證件及一張字條。有街坊稱，昨日傍晚6時已見到該些財物。<br />\n<br />\n已經否定劫殺？"},{"pid":"88940ee84d36a72c4f794251d8345871a011fff8","tid":264671,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:04:19.000Z","msg":"慶祝端午節？"},{"pid":"3b9627988a21dc505ff0bd43602bc2b822b1f78a","tid":264671,"uid":119832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:06:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>慶祝端午節？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  進取型糉"},{"pid":"6c19be9b08f321bf0c5b52b2987005efe0dc604e","tid":264671,"uid":5462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:08:26.000Z","msg":"似自殺"},{"pid":"51f4ff0d7e19554ed1b1de708d88674a46ebc0e4","tid":264671,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:08:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁撚樣都無可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n屈原又屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ae52df6b911c40330a7c8e55c404153ef1cb97","tid":264671,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:09:14.000Z","msg":"巴打講過棄屍一定係棄大海一來身份難辨認,二來搜識困難所以黑警通常都唔會查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"